Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 445
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=Corruption
  - 108
By: The Blessed Virgin at Fatima
Commentary: By this must be understood the appetitive, demiurgic,
  centrifugal character of the creative impulse, which as a separative
  force, is at the root of all remotion from Principle. In other words,
  Creation and the Fall both share a 'sexual' motivation, exalted from
  one aspect and disastrous from another. But it can also be a unifying
  power.
---
More souls go to hell because of sins of the flesh than for any other
reason.
